title: Southbridge Townhome,  Fairfield
posting_body: ['122 Brogan Ct.', ' Extremely well-maintained condo in the desirable Southbridge townhomes.', 'Located off of Waterman Blvd.', 'in the West Side of Fairfield.', 'Upgraded flooring throughout-- laminate in living areas & kitchen & plush carpet in bedrooms.', 'Ample storage in closets, cabinets and garage.', 'Walk-in master bedroom closet.', 'Custom, built-in organization in pantry and one bedroom closet.', 'Kitchen has tile counter tops and stainless-steel appliances.', '5 burner gas range in kitchen.', 'Open floor plan for the dining area, living room and kitchen (great for entertaining)!', 'Spacious bedrooms.', 'Double sinks in master bathroom.', 'No landscaping to maintain!', 'Small back patio area.', 'Community pool maintained by HOA.', 'Great location near I-80 for an easy commute, Rancho Solano Golf course and shopping.', 'Refrigerator, but not under warranty.', "Don't miss out!", 'No pets.', 'Appointments coming soon.', 'Must apply to view.', '(WE DO NOT RESPOND TO EMAIL)', 'TO DOWNLOAD AN APPLICATION OR TO SEE ALL OF OUR RENTALS PLEASE GO TO: <URL>', 'Applications accepted now call the office to find out how.', 'Camellia Realty', '2801 Waterman Blvd.', '#150', 'Fairfield, CA', 'show contact info', 'Hours: 9-4 Mon-Thurs', '9-1 Friday', 'Closed Saturday and Sunday', 'Availability, terms and prices subject to change without notice.']
